latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Here’s a look at a day in my life with my Honda Amaze ! I have to say, it is a dream to drive. One push engine start and I am good to go. Plus, it has so many stylish details like the premium stitch fabric seats, C-shaped LED lights, the dashboard. Best of all, the touch screen DIGIPAD and handsfree telephone makes my life super simple. And lastly, that big boot space? That’s a saviour when it comes to my shopping trips– truly an Amaze-ing experience!

latestPosts.caption:
We made it! 🎉 Yes, we made it to @forbesindia Top 100 Digital Creators! 😍 I feel so blessed.

I can hardly put into words how this feels—coming from a small town to standing here today feels like a dream come true. 🌟 Every like, comment, and share has been a part of this journey, and I owe it all to YOU—my incredible audience. 🙏 Together, we’ve turned passion into something extraordinary. Thank you for making this happen—this is our win! ✨

Thank you Amma, Acha, @thatmallupenn @thatmalluchekkan  for always being there for me.🫂 Thank you @monkentertainment 💛
